e is consumed; or imprisonment, from one to three years, if a suicide attempt results in a serious bodily injury.\n**'''Sole paragraph''' - The penalty is doubled:\n* Increased penalty\n** I - if the crime is committed for selfish motive;\n** II - if the victim is less or has decreased, for any reason, the capacity of resistance.\n* Infanticide\n|headerstyle=background:#ccccff\n|style=text-align:center;\n}}\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.jusbrasil.com.br/topicos/10625219/artigo-122-do-decreto-lei-n-2848-de-07-de-dezembro-de-1940 |publisher=Jusbrasil|title=Artigo 122 C\u00f3digo Penal |accessdate=2017-11-09}}</ref>\n<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/decreto-lei/Del2848compilado.htm |publisher=Government of Brazil |title=C\u00f3digo Penal |accessdate=2017-11-09}}</ref>\n|-\n|''{{flag|British Virgin Islands}}''\n| {{unknown}}\n| {{unknown}}\n| {{unknown}}\n| {{unknown}}\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Canada}}\n| {{yes|Legal}}\n| {{yes|Legal medical assisted suicide}}\n| {{yes|Legal}}\n|[[Euthanasia in Canada]]\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://scc-csc.lexum.com/scc-csc/scc-csc/en/item/14637/index.do |publisher=Government of Canada |title=Carter v. Canada (Attorney General) |accessdate=2016-08-13}}</ref><ref>[http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/supreme-court-gives-parliament-4-month-extension-on-doctor-assisted-dying-law-1.2739275 Supreme court gives Parliament 4-month extension on doctor-assisted dying law |CTV News<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>\n|-\n|''{{flag|Cayman Islands}}''\n| {{yes|Legal}}\n| {{no|Illegal}}\n| {{no|Illegal}}\n| {{hidden\n|Article 187. Suicide pacts\n|(1) It shall be manslaughter and not murder for a person acting in pursuance of a suicide pact between him and another to kill the other or to be a party to the other killing himself or being killed by a third person. \n|headerstyle=background:#ccccff\n|style=text-align:center;\n}}\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gov.ky/portal/pls/portal/docs/1/11525775.PDF |publisher=Government of the C